<h2 id="dvla-board">DVLA board</h2>

<p>At the heart of its corporate governance; the agency has a board lead by a non executive chair, with the chief executive and the agencyâ€™s functional directors serving as members. In addition three non executive directors have been appointed whose role is to challenge and to mentor, each drawing upon their perspective as private citizens but each with skill sets gained from senior positions in the private sector.</p>

<p>The board has both strategic and business oversight responsibilities.</p>
